attributes.Long form description: The student is assembling a black shelf. First, he puts together the curved tubes and align the black bases on the table. Then, he assembles the legs into the base and screws them in place. Next, he places the shelf on the bottom and assembles the black brackets on the side. Finally,  he screws the wheels onto the bottom and inspects the finished product.
